ONE-LINE SUMMARY
=========================================================

C++ casts provide controlled type conversion:
- static_cast → compile-time safe conversion
- dynamic_cast → runtime safe polymorphic conversion
- const_cast → remove constness
- reinterpret_cast → low-level unsafe memory reinterpretation
